headline: Weyerhaeuser Company Declares Dividend on Common Shares, Completes Existing Share Repurchase Program and Authorizes New $1 Billion Share Repurchase Program
summary: Weyerhaeuser Company (NYSE: WY) today announced that its board of directors declared a quarterly base cash dividend of $0.21 per share on the common stock of the company, payable in cash on June 13, 2025, to holders of record of such common stock as of the close of business on May 30, 2025.

headline: Weyerhaeuser: Hold These Irreplaceable Real Estate Assets
summary: Weyerhaeuser, a leading timberland REIT, owns 10.5 million acres of U.S. timberlands, excelling in sustainable forest management and wood product production.
